\begin_inset Formula $0.739083847\ldots$
\end_inset

.
 And no matter how many times you repeat, or iterate, the calculation, it
 won't change much.
 In fact, once it reaches 
\begin_inset Formula $0.7390851332\ldots$
\end_inset

, it won't change at all (unless your calculator shows more decimal places—after
 about 90 iterations, a calculator showing 15 decimal places will display
 
\begin_inset Formula $0.739085133215161$
\end_inset

