\begin_inset Formula $\sqrt[3]{\frac{\sqrt{13}x^{2}+10x^{2}\text{−}\frac{10\sqrt{13}x}{3}\text{−}\frac{50x}{3}+\frac{4\sqrt{13}}{3}+\frac{38}{3}}{2}}$
\end_inset

.
